Here is a simple portfolio template using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript in three separate files. It includes a background color, animation effects, and sections for About Me, Skills, and Projects.


---

✅ 1️⃣. index.html

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Hemalatha S Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"/>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1 class="animated-text">Hemalatha S - Web Developer</h1>
    </header>

    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>Hello! I'm Hemalatha S, a passionate web developer focused on building interactive and beautiful web applications using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="skills">
        <h2>Skills</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>HTML, CSS, JavaScript</li>
            <li>Responsive Web Design</li>
            <li>Animation Effects</li>
            <li>Problem Solving</li>
            <li>Frontend Development</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="projects">
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <div class="project-list">
            <div class="project-item">📱 Portfolio Website</div>
            <div class="project-item">🛠️ Todo List App</div>
            <div class="project-item">🎨 Interactive Gallery</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>Contact: Shilpa06211@gmail.com</p>
        <p>© 2025 Hemalatha S</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>


